OL,3,CJunior doctors start 72-hour strike in
OL,4,Crow over pay and working conditions
OL,6,FJunior doctors in Wales are walking
OL,7,Fout for the second time in a row over
OL,8,Fpay and working conditions.
OL,10,Fstarted at 7am this morning (Wednesday
OL,11,F21 February) and will last three days
OL,12,Fafter an identical walkout in January.
OL,14,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,15,Fin Wales decided to ballot members in
OL,16,FAugust with almost 98% voting in
OL,17,Ffavour of industrial action.
OL,19,FDr Peter Fahey, co-chair of the Welsh
OL,20,FBMA junior doctors committee, said:
OL,21,F"No doctor wants to go on strike.
