OL,6,F"We signed up to do this, we studied
OL,7,Ffor years, have up to #100,000 student
OL,8,Fdebt - we've chosen to do this job and
OL,9,Fyet the Government has pushed us so
OL,10,Ffar that we are walking out, we don't
OL,11,Fwant to do this."
OL,13,FDr Peter Fahey continued: "Doctors are
OL,14,Fangry, they feel let down. I think
OL,15,Fit's been clear that these are doctors
OL,16,Fthat have gone into a pandemic with no
OL,17,Fknowledge, no PPE, anything.
