OL,6,F"They're on the front line and they've
OL,7,Fbeen let down, they've had a further
OL,8,Freal-time pay cut since the start of
OL,9,Fthe pandemic."
OL,11,FJunior doctors want to see their
OL,12,Fstarting pay increase from #13.65 an
OL,13,Fhour to #19 an hour.
OL,15,FThe Welsh Government has offered a 5%
OL,16,Fpay rise, described as the worst in
OL,17,Fthe UK, and said it cannot offer more
OL,18,Fmoney without additional funding.
