OL,6,FDr Fahey added: "The 5% pay offer this
OL,7,Fyear is just a further insult to these
OL,8,Fdoctors. It's another real-terms pay
OL,9,Fcut and does nothing to address the
OL,10,F30% of pay erosion that we've had
OL,11,Fsince 2008."
OL,13,Fis a devolved issue in Wales, meaning
OL,14,Fresponsibility for pay, waiting lists,
OL,15,Fand budgets falls to the Labour
OL,16,Fadministration.
OL,18,FThe head of NHS Wales, Judith Paget,
OL,19,Fhas urged everyone to on the NHS by
OL,20,Fconsidering other options to attending
OL,21,Fhospital unless they need urgent care.
