OL,6,FHealth Minister said further talks are
OL,7,Fwelcomed, but that the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment does not have the budget
OL,9,Favailable to increase the pay deal.
OL,11,F"We are disappointed that junior
OL,12,Fdoctors have decided to take further
OL,13,Findustrial action in Wales, but we
OL,14,Funderstand their strength of feeling
OL,15,Fabout our 5% pay offer," Ms Morgan
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"Our offer is at the limits of the
OL,19,Ffinances available to us and reflects
OL,20,Fthe position reached with the other
OL,21,Fhealth unions."
