OL,3,CJunior doctors start 72-hour strike in
OL,4,Crow over pay and working conditions
OL,6,FThe Health Minister said she will
OL,7,Fcontinue to press the UK Government to
OL,8,Fpass on the funding necessary for
OL,9,F"full and fair pay rises" for public
OL,10,Fsector workers.
OL,12,FThe UK Government has previously said
OL,13,Fthat Wales has received a record level
OL,14,Fof funding this year.
OL,16,FDuring the industrial action in
OL,17,FJanuary 41% per cent of outpatient
OL,18,Fappointments and 61% of operations
OL,19,Fwere postponed across Wales.
